  "raw_meta_yaml": "schema_version: 1\n\ncontext:\n  version: \"1.6.3\"\n\npackage:\n  name: ${{ \"soqt6\" if build_variant == \"qt6\" else \"soqt\" }}\n  version: ${{ version }}\n\nsource:\n  url: https://github.com/coin3d/soqt/releases/download/v${{ version }}/soqt-${{ version }}-src.tar.gz\n  sha256: 79342e89290783457c075fb6a60088aad4a48ea072ede06fdf01985075ef46bd\n  patches:\n    - if: linux\n      then:\n        - patches/gl_private_linking.patch\n\nbuild:\n  number: 4\n  script: build\n\nrequirements:\n  run_exports:\n    - ${{ pin_subpackage('soqt6' if build_variant == 'qt6' else 'soqt', upper_bound='x.x.x') }}\n  build:\n    - ${{ compiler('cxx') }}\n    - ${{ stdlib('c') }}\n    - if: build_platform != target_platform and build_variant == \"qt6\"\n      then: qt6-main\n    - if: build_platform != target_platform and build_variant == \"qt5\"\n      then: qt-main\n    - ninja\n    - cmake <4\n  host:\n    - if: build_variant == \"qt6\"\n      then: qt6-main\n    - if: build_variant == \"qt5\"\n      then: qt-main\n    - coin3d\n    - if: linux\n      then: libgl-devel\n  run_constraints:\n    - if: build_variant == \"qt6\"\n      then: soqt <0\n    - if: build_variant == \"qt5\"\n      then: soqt6 <0\n\ntests:\n  - if: unix\n    then:\n      - script: run_test.sh\n        files:\n          recipe:\n            - CMakeLists.txt\n        requirements:\n          build:\n            - cmake\n            - ninja\n            - ${{ compiler(\"cxx\") }}\n            - if: linux\n              then: libgl-devel\n  - if: win\n    then:\n      - script: run_test.bat\n        files:\n          recipe:\n            - CMakeLists.txt\n        requirements:\n          build:\n            - cmake\n            - ninja\n            - ${{ compiler(\"cxx\") }}\n\nabout:\n  homepage: https://github.com/coin3d/soqt\n  license: BSD-3-Clause\n  license_file: COPYING\n  summary: SoQt library needed by Coin3d.\n  description: |\n    SoQt is a Qt GUI component toolkit library for Coin. It is also compatible with SGI and TGS Open Inventor,\n    and the API is based on the API of the InventorXt GUI component toolkit.\n  documentation: https://github.com/coin3d/soqt\n  repository: https://github.com/coin3d/soqt\n\nextra:\n  recipe-maintainers:\n    - looooo\n",
